      <section eId="sec_49_3_2">
        <num>49-3-2</num>
        <content>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1937, p. 355, § 10; Ga. L. 1963, p. 222, § 1; Ga. L. 1981, p. 960, § 1; Ga. L. 1988, p. 1354, § 1; Ga. L. 1994, p. 505, § 1; Ga. L. 2015, p. 552, § 2/SB 138; Ga. L. 2016, p. 376, § 1/HB 765; Ga. L. 2017, p. 774, § 49/HB 323.)</p>
          <p>The 2015 amendment,
      effective July 1, 2015, rewrote this Code section.</p>
          <p>The 2016 amendment,
      effective July 1, 2016, added ", active or retired" at the end of paragraphs (a)(1) through (a)(5), (a)(7), and (a)(9).</p>
          <p>The 2017 amendment,
      effective May 9, 2017, part of an Act to revise, modernize, and correct the Code, revised capitalization throughout subsection (e).</p>
        </content>
      </section>
